{"word":"G1941 - ἐπικαλέομαι - epikaléomai - ep-ee-kal-eh'-om-ahee - Appeal","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπικαλέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>epikaléomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-kal-eh'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Appeal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொழுதுகொள், அபயமிடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to put a name upon, to surname"},{"paragraph":"2. to call something to one"},{"paragraph":"3. to call upon to invoke"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G2564 - καλέω - kaléō - kal-eh'-o/2564\">G2564</a>; to <i>entitle</i>; by implication to <i>invoke</i> (for aid, worship, testimony, decision, etc.): - appeal (unto), call (on, upon), surname."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1458 - ἐγκαλέω - enkaléō - eng-kal-eh'-o/1458\">G1458</a>, <a href=\"#/G1462 - ἔγκλημα - énklēma - eng'-klay-mah/1462\">G1462</a>, <a href=\"#/G1528 - εἰσκαλέω - eiskaléō - ice-kal-eh'-o/1528\">G1528</a>, <a href=\"#/G1577 - ἐκκλησία - ekklēsía - ek-klay-see'-ah/1577\">G1577</a>, <a href=\"#/G1941 - ἐπικαλέομαι - epikaléomai - ep-ee-kal-eh'-om-ahee/1941\">G1941</a>, <a href=\"#/G2564 - καλέω - kaléō - kal-eh'-o/2564\">G2564</a>, <a href=\"#/G2821 - κλῆσις - klēsis - klay'-sis/2821\">G2821</a>, <a href=\"#/G2822 - κλητός - klētós - klay-tos'/2822\">G2822</a>, <a href=\"#/G3333 - μετακαλέω - metakaléō - met-ak-al-eh'-o/3333\">G3333</a>, <a href=\"#/G4292 - προκαλέομαι - prokaléomai - prok-al-eh'-om-ahee/4292\">G4292</a>, <a href=\"#/G4341 - προσκαλέομαι - proskaléomai - pros-kal-eh'-om-ahee/4341\">G4341</a>, <a href=\"#/G4779 - συγκαλέω - synkaléō - soong-kal-eh'-o/4779\">G4779</a>, <a href=\"#/G479 - ἀντικαλέω - antikaléō - an-tee-kal-eh'-o/479\">G479</a>"}]}